snippet.title: Elemental Dog Defense Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Get it on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/3087110/Elemental_Dog_Defense/
Join our Discord!   https://discord.com/invite/8QZCtyndHn 
A PvP Tower Defense game where you transmute and deploy elemental Dogs to devise the ultimate strategy for each battle.
